        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-2022a744-8751-47d1-9ed9-2f94cea85d9f">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-2022a744-8751-47d1-9ed9-2f94cea85d9f">
                Mr. Stokes
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2022a744-8751-47d1-9ed9-2f94cea85d9f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-10-08/debates/02b24e7a-e874-4c10-8379-049dc6e6d4eb/ScientificAdvisoryCouncil#contribution-2022a744-8751-47d1-9ed9-2f94cea85d9f">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the right hon. Gentleman aware that the constitution of the Scientific Advisory Council was announced after I put the Question down? Will he say whether the presidents of these institutions were taken into consultation in any way?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2022a744-8751-47d1-9ed9-2f94cea85d9f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-10-08/debates/02b24e7a-e874-4c10-8379-049dc6e6d4eb/ScientificAdvisoryCouncil#contribution-2022a744-8751-47d1-9ed9-2f94cea85d9f">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-e6ea2f53-6808-4490-bcf7-fe4d803d66c3">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-e6ea2f53-6808-4490-bcf7-fe4d803d66c3">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-e6ea2f53-6808-4490-bcf7-fe4d803d66c3">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-e6ea2f53-6808-4490-bcf7-fe4d803d66c3">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e6ea2f53-6808-4490-bcf7-fe4d803d66c3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-10-08/debates/02b24e7a-e874-4c10-8379-049dc6e6d4eb/ScientificAdvisoryCouncil#contribution-e6ea2f53-6808-4490-bcf7-fe4d803d66c3">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am sure there were numerous consultations, but I could not say exactly which scientific leaders were consulted. I believe that the Advisory Council commands the support and acceptance of the scientific world.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
